Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:05.01,tuduku,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\pos(556,353)}未完待續
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.12,0:00:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.50,0:00:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我去趟小賣部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.84,0:00:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那我先開動了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.08,0:00:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,高中開始大概一個月
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.80,0:00:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\an8}這個好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.01,0:00:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\an8}你們知道我為了搞到這件衣服吃了多少苦頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.42,0:00:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,起初支配班級的不安和拘束的緊張感逐漸緩和
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,大家各自在班裡找到了自己的歸屬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.35,0:00:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,開始摸索出自己與同學間的距離感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,而這傢伙毫無疑問踏入了中二病的黑暗面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.51,0:00:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,小鳥遊同學  你的便當份量一直都好大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.74,0:00:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,戰鬥需要充分的補給
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,魔力不夠充盈  可是會危及生命的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.97,0:00:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛  我那個時候也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,既然身處戰鬥之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.59,0:00:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,進食必須速戰速決
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:00:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好欠揍…那時候的我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.08,0:00:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這便當還真驚人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,既然身處戰鬥之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,進食必須得到保證
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.63,0:01:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,別說一樣的台詞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.91,0:01:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.62,0:01:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,聖調理人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.08,0:01:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,誒…十花小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.49,0:01:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,人不可貌相  廚藝很不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.03,0:01:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,「誒…人不可貌相」我會這麼轉達的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.31,0:01:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,轉達就不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.93,0:01:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,聖調理人為了隱藏真實身份
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.16,0:01:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在現實世界以廚師的身份活動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣的人做的便當的話  肯定相當…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.81,0:01:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,紅色的果實會降低魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.88,0:01:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,這個尤其危險
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.79,0:01:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就是說  你不喜歡吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.57,0:01:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,特別是這個綠色的顆粒非常棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.24,0:01:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,吃這種東西的人肯定不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.58,0:01:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕這就是魔獸之卵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.90,0:01:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,快向種番茄的農民伯伯道歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.19,0:01:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  米飯有被侵蝕的跡象
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.46,0:02:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,真拿你沒辦法  我幫你吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.74,0:02:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,這莫非是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.18,0:02:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.21,0:02:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是你們想的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.23,0:02:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Death
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}（社團說明會）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.73,0:04:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來是空手道部的示範表演
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂  勇太打算選哪個社團
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  感覺哪裡都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我打從一開始就決定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,輕音部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,誒…你喜歡音樂的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.43,0:04:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,說什麼呢  哪有男生因為喜歡音樂才進輕音部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,搖滾是為何而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,電子吉他又是為何而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯  為了受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都是為了受女生歡迎而存在的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.90,0:04:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你這真是相當的偏見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.78,0:04:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不  應該說是「不受歡迎情結」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,告別了國中棒球部時代的和尚頭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.52,0:04:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好不容易走到今天這一步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,兩個月後一定左肩背吉他  右手牽女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,左後方還有另一個傾慕我的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,社團嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.07,0:04:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(385,328)}Rendezvous  Point
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.47,0:05:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,結束之後  前往會合地點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.68,0:05:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,枯葉的墓碑處  六花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我才沒聽說過那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,幹嘛像告白一樣地等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這個好像可以當武器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,然後  有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,時間有限
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我就直說了  希望你能認真聽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.39,0:05:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我想在這所學校裡設立我們的據點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,據點？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.71,0:05:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,想設立新的社團
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,太過於脫離現實  以至於無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:05:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,能再說一次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:05:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Pepero  via  vaniste
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思  不小心用了平行世界的語言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那是和這個世界的文字呈鏡面文字關係的語言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,無聊的解說就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你剛才說什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,在這所學校設立社團  作為我們活動的據點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,名字是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.26,0:06:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,遠東…魔術…結社
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,請努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.61,0:06:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,用正常方法叫住我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,總之在這裡寫上名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得我會寫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.56,0:06:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,果然嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了  沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我做副部長就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.69,0:06:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,勇太來做部長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.19,0:06:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,重點不是那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:06:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,再說  有別人願意入部了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這個你不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:06.57,post,,0,0,0,,{\pos(236,92)}招收部員
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:06.57,post,,0,0,0,,{\pos(208,208)}遠東魔術
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:06.57,post,,0,0,0,,{\pos(208,237)}結社
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:06.57,post,,0,0,0,,{\pos(231,335)}請排成一列。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼誰都不感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這是當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是境界線管理局的魔術師們在進行妨礙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,住手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都躲得遠遠了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,請問  有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.25,0:07:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,勇太  交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你也太認生了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,根據我的邪王真眼觀察
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,邪王？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你身上傳來不祥的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,想要將之驅除  需要借用黑暗的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,進入我遠東魔術結社  用邪王真眼的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這種手法已經完全出局了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  全都是胡說的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:07:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.59,0:08:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  真巧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,午睡部？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  有興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.29,0:08:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,午睡很不錯哦  很有意思哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,沒  沒什麼興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.34,0:08:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都這麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,去年也想建立來著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.78,0:08:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道為什麼招不到人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.26,0:08:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,隨身枕頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.76,0:08:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  今天天氣晴朗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,春季晴天用枕頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,枕著這個能夢見草原呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs16}（遠東魔術午睡結社）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺越來越讓人難以靠近了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,放眼一片碧綠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真的夢見草原了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,情況之所以沒有好轉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:09:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是這裡魔術係數的問題嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.84,0:09:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,丹生谷？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.44,0:09:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我去趟洗手間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.84,0:09:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,這身裝扮  絕對是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,大家不要勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.37,0:09:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,來了啊  我就知道你會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.43,0:09:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你會在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,丹生谷森夏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,來啦啦隊部體驗入部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼難得的事件怎麼能錯過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你看  班裡裝作偶然路過的男生們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.39,0:09:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,真有人氣啊  丹生谷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,她可是班裡男生全員投票「可愛女生錦標賽」NO.1啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,NO.1嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.22,0:09:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,難道說你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  沒沒  那怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.39,0:09:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,偶然視線對上了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.39,0:09:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,小鳥遊同學也在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,這還真是走運
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.08,0:09:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:10:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,她說想試試像啦啦隊員那樣一躍而起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我要說自己是新生的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,會不會也能讓我試試呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.06,0:10:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,在圍繞著不可視境界線的戰鬥中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.87,0:10:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我在那邊的世界數千米高的高空飛行過  沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,這孩子在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣  跳得起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不太行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.38,0:10:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.27,0:10:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,小…小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,沒哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,才怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,此路不通  吃我一波
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.63,0:10:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是演劇部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.08,0:10:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,十年未見的母親病危
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,請務必放我過去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:10:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,這是即興表演
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,為了擴展演技領域  進行即興劇目的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是獨木橋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.13,0:11:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,寬度只容許一個人通過的獨木橋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,兩人站在橋的兩側
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,然後以即興表演來讓對方先給自己讓路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,如果對方放你過去了就算贏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.96,0:11:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,想要過此橋  就先打倒我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  不是對你說的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.40,0:11:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,要試試看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起  能讓我先過去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不抓緊的話  他乘坐的飛機就要起飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不趁現在當面傳達心意的話  從此就天各一方了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.27,0:11:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,哼  垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.69,0:11:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,熊來了  趕緊逃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,以吾之邪王真眼討伐之
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,快躲開！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.26,0:12:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,328)}Schwarz  Sechs  Prototype  Mark  II
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.26,0:12:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,漆黑澤克斯原始型二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,想要過此橋  就先打倒我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.71,0:12:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,328)}Dark  Matter  Blaze
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.71,0:12:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,暗物質火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這不算什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.11,0:12:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然擋住了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.57,0:12:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到會在這種地方遇見光明陣營的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,可以讓開了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,突破
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.73,0:12:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,別鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.99,0:12:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,明明已經展示了我們比其他社團更加優秀但卻沒人來…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不得已  沒想到需要召喚她…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,六花  你有可以找的人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.98,0:12:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,紅衣主教開始行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,因為羅馬教廷魔術結社的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,現在狀況已經「省略一萬字」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:12:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,馬上跟我碰面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你剛才清清楚楚地說了「省略一萬字」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,明天她會與我會合
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,滿是不好的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,突然找你出來真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.10,0:13:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  找我有事是指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.62,0:13:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,太難以啟齒了  所以我只說一遍哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我…對富樫君…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,對我？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,L-O-V-E
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Love~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好癢…好癢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.60,0:13:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了…知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.52,0:13:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,終於甦醒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,328)}Dark·Flame  Master
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,漆黑烈焰使
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,在問別人名字之前  你是不是該先報上名來？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.63,0:13:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我說…我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.16,0:14:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,在說之前請先放開我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.67,0:14:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(471,328)}Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.67,0:14:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,邪王真眼使——小鳥遊六花的第一僕從
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(260,328)}Mjolnir  Hammer
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,雷霆戰鎚使——凸守早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這廂有禮！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.09,0:14:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裡來的回哪裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我的僕從
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,勇太的精神已經受到管理局魔術的侵蝕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,因此偶爾會做出奇怪的舉動  希望你能諒解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.69,0:14:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,確實  眼神和墮落的普通人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,果然還是給你一槍如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就由我凸守來淨化你的心靈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,328)}Mjolnir  Tornado
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,雷鎚颶風
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,動不了了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙…是真正的笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼  平行世界那邊如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.46,0:14:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,戰事仍在不斷升級
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:15:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,凸守也想盡可能多地加入到戰鬥中去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.95,0:15:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  特地讓你過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但這對於找到不可視境界線有重要作用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.77,0:15:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.73,0:15:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,兩人一唱一和  這愚蠢的對話永無止境…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你這身制服…難道是我們學校國中部的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.63,0:15:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(181,328)}Second  Children
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.63,0:15:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(301,328)}Third  Children
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.63,0:15:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,第二適格者和第三適格者的年齡是一樣的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼一臉開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.99,0:15:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(350,328)}Electrical  Ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.99,0:15:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我和凸守是兩年前在電磁海洋中產生共鳴的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,並得知她前世便是我的僕從
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說在網上認識的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.71,0:15:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我會讓凸守加入遠東魔術午睡結社
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣部員就有四人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,然後  建部所需的第五個人就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼才會認同吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,放學後  你帶奇美拉一起來學校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.49,0:15:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要佔領據點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這實在太勉強了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:16:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,貓可不能被算作部員哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.92,0:16:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但是奇美拉是我的僕從
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,和凸守是同等的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.64,0:16:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯  它和凸守一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你倒是否定一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.91,0:16:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,要是再有一個人就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,其實是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.82,0:16:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但那裡有一隻願意幫助我們的幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.51,0:16:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  的確
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,還真有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,學姐你別也瞎起哄啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,而且  其實我身體裡還有另一具人格
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,等等…好像要出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh…nice  to  meet  you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我是凱瑟琳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這孩子身體中的另一具人格
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.76,0:16:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,請問凱瑟琳小姐是哪國人士？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.12,0:16:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你也跟著鬧嗎  小七
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.85,0:16:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,本來的我是在十八世紀的英國出生的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh…Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,連學姐也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice  to  meet  you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.89,0:16:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.04,0:17:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,328)}What  do  you  think  of  Rikka?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.04,0:17:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得六花怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,請再說一遍…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,328)}What  do  you  think  of  Rikka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得六花怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.18,0:17:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh…yes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,用…用日語就行…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.49,0:17:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,328)}It's  easy  for  you  to  talk  in  English,  right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.49,0:17:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,用英語談對你很容易吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.90,0:17:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛…眼睛…眼睛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.75,0:17:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼果然還是不能把她算作部員哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.99,0:17:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,小七  表面裝作天然但其實善於智取！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  這樣也未免太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.86,0:17:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,雖說沒有魔力反應
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但也有可能做了偽裝  所以多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.90,0:17:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,七瀨老師真體貼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.16,0:17:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到她說只要打掃完這裡  就將我們算作同好會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:17:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒覺得我們更像是在被巧妙利用罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我要再次確認一下你是否有資格當我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.07,0:18:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,小鳥遊六花…不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,邪王真眼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.97,0:18:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,若沒有這份氣勢  你也就無法勝任我的僕從一職
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.48,0:18:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,放馬過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,爆裂吧  現實
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,崩斷吧  神經
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,328)}Vanishment  this  world
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,消失吧  這個世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.13,0:18:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,328)}Lunatic  Mjolnir  Crusher
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.13,0:18:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,瘋狂雷鎚碾壓者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,328)}Judgement  Lucifer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,路西法審判
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,328)}Eternal  Salamander  G
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,永恆火蜥G
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.69,0:19:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,328)}Royal  Revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.69,0:19:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,王室革命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,328)}Laplace  Soffiava
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,拉普拉斯風暴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.24,0:19:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你們給我適可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,真是花了好長時間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,有這麼髒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不…說來話長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.64,0:19:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼既然完成任務了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就幫你們以同好會的名義提出申請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.21,0:19:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了  朝思暮想的午睡部！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,就用剛打掃完的教室作為活動室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.53,0:19:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,今後就請努力升格為「社團」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:19:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,社團活動從明天開始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.14,0:19:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,請務必做好準備
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是  My  Master
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,勇太也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我可從來沒說過要入部哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.88,0:20:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,什…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧…難道富樫君你欺騙了我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.51,0:20:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,學姐  你鬧得越來越像六花了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,幹嘛真這麼失落啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼如此拘泥於我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係  大可不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(260,328)}Mabinogion
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,根據「黑暗聖典」的七色抄本上所述
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.42,0:20:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,漆黑烈焰使終究會服從於邪王真眼的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這又是什麼怪書
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(220,328)}Electrical  Ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(451,328)}Mori  Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這是凸守在電磁海洋上找到的由魔術師森大人寫的書哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,0:20:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,世間萬象都在此書中有詳細說明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,騙小孩呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這個好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.47,0:20:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,只要擁有此書  一切都瞭如指掌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,鏘鏘~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.08,0:21:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.06,0:21:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣  心動了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,才不會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.38,0:21:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就行的話  根本就不用辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.17,0:21:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛嘛  別著急啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.56,0:21:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,說起來  聽說你加入了一個奇怪的同好會？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.65,0:21:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,才沒加入呢  絕對沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.87,0:21:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,誒  但聽說是叫遠東什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說根本沒加入  也不打算加入
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,富樫君~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.69,0:21:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,可以打擾一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.17,0:21:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.90,0:21:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要加入富樫君的同好會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.38,0:21:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,現在來交入部申請書了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.93,0:21:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,誒…不是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.99,0:21:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.59,0:21:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,為了表達我的感謝之意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.50,0:21:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我更慎重地考慮了一下社團的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.98,0:21:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,遠東魔術午睡結社
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.43,0:21:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,…之夏？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.11,0:22:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不是…吧
